<h1 class="doc-page-title">Demand Management</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">Comprehensive demand management system for capturing, triaging, prioritising, and tracking new work requests across the DfE digital portfolio.</p>

<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

<p>Demand management in COMPASS enables teams to capture new work requests, assess their impact and strategic alignment, triage them through governance meetings, prioritise them based on scoring, and convert approved requests into projects for delivery tracking.</p>

